WEBVTT

00:04:57.170 --> 00:05:00.717
Hakuna mtu hapa anaweza kutuhumiwa
au kumjua Narcissus.

00:05:00.717 --> 00:05:03.013
(Kicheko)

00:05:03.013 --> 00:05:05.581
Lakini unapofikira kuhusu Narcissus,

00:05:05.581 --> 00:05:09.661
usipende tumuonekano wako mwenyewe.

00:05:09.661 --> 00:05:11.452
Mwisho, kutoka kwa Muamerika wa Kusini:

00:05:11.452 --> 00:05:14.213
Huyu ni mshairi maarufu Jorge Luis Borges.

00:05:14.213 --> 00:05:15.402
Alipotishiwa na majambazi

00:05:15.402 --> 00:05:18.035
wa jeshi la serikali ya Argentina,

00:05:18.035 --> 00:05:20.288
alirudi na kusema, "Ah, wacha nawe,

00:05:20.288 --> 00:05:23.733
utatisha vipi, kama sio kwa kifo?"

00:05:23.733 --> 00:05:26.853
Kitu cha kuvutia, kitu cha asili,

00:05:26.853 --> 00:05:30.045
ilikua kutishia mtu na ukosefu wa maadili.